{
  "texts": [
    "For instance, LogTrans [49] introduces a dedicated decoder for IMS forecasting, while Informer [12] leverages a generative-style decoder.",
    "Additionally, Pyraformer [70] incorporates a fully connected layer that concatenates spatiotemporal axes as its decoder.",
    "Autoformer [67] adds the two refined decomposition features of the trend-cyclical components and the stacked autocorrelation mechanism of the seasonal component to obtain the final prediction results.",
    "Similarly, FEDformer [79] applies a decomposition scheme and employs the proposed frequency attention block in deciphering the final results.",
    "ConclusionTransformer architecture has been found to be applicable to solving various time-series tasks."
  ]
}